        "content": "<p>Kinda found it when tinkering with math from <a class=\"stream-topic\" data-stream-id=\"113489\" href=\"/#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/Criterion.20for.20equality.20in.20the.20triangle.20inequality.20for.20angles/with/537567514\">#new members &gt; Criterion for equality in the triangle inequality for angles</a>.</p>",
